data.text: @ScrtNrdPrincess You can try a cold compress on your arm.
@NinaNighting @ShnoodOlaf I hope so too! I only know one person who got symptoms later, so I'm not completely outta the woods, but it's looking positive.
@ScrtNrdPrincess @ShnoodOlaf Hopefully you are already through the worst of it!

@ShnoodOlaf I was completely prepped to feel much worse so I can't complain. I made chicken noodle soup and bought oranges and 3 different kinds of juices plus Propel and Pedialyte, mostly nectar I'm a big baby when I'm sick. But I've been super hydrating so I think that's helped.
@ScrtNrdPrincess Glad to hear you're not miserable! Keep hydrating and pop some ibuprofen. Hoping you will start feeling better through the day!!
